						"text": "рҹ”Ҙ **WELCOME TO PARENTAL PANGEA** рҹ”Ҙ\r\n\r\nThis world was never meant to become this.\r\n\r\nOnce, everything was controlled вҖ”\r\nbalanced systems, predictable ecosystems, stable progression.\r\n\r\nThen something changed.\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nThe ARK systems began to fail.\r\n\r\nNot all at onceвҖҰ but enough.\r\n\r\nEnough to corrupt evolution.\r\nEnough to destabilize technology.\r\nEnough to turn survival into something far more dangerous.\r\n\r\nThey call it:\r\n\r\nрҹ©ё **PRIMAL CHAOS**\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nCreatures no longer follow natural limits.\r\nPower comes at a cost.\r\nAnd the world itself pushes back against those who underestimate it.\r\n\r\nThis is not a place of safety.\r\n\r\nThis is a place of adaptation.\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nвҡ”пёҸ **WHAT YOUвҖҷRE STEPPING INTO**\r\nвҖў A progression system shaped by Primal Chaos\r\nвҖў A survival experience built around efficiency and balance\r\nвҖў Systems designed to reward smart play вҖ” not excess\r\nвҖў A cluster optimized for performance, not clutter\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nрҹ§  **SURVIVAL HERE IS DIFFERENT**\r\n\r\nThis world doesnвҖҷt favor the biggest base.\r\nIt doesnвҖҷt reward the largest army.\r\n\r\nIt rewards those who:\r\nвҖў Adapt quickly\r\nвҖў Build intelligently\r\nвҖў Respect the limits of the system\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nрҹ”Ҙ **EVERYTHING HAS CONSEQUENCES**\r\n\r\nOverbuild, and you weaken yourself.\r\nOverfarm, and you fall behind.\r\nUnderestimate the worldвҖҰ and it will end you.\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nрҹ’Җ **THIS IS YOUR CHALLENGE**\r\n\r\nThere are no guarantees here.\r\nNo shortcuts. No safety nets.\r\n\r\nOnly opportunity.\r\n\r\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\r\n\r\nрҹ”Ҙ **SURVIVE THE CHAOS**\r\n\r\nAdapt. Build. Dominate.\r\n\r\n**Welcome to Parental Pangea.**\r\n"
